  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The equation above models the number of members,&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">M,</span> of a gym <span class=\"italic\">t</span> years after the gym opens. Of the following, which equation models the number of members of the gym <span class=\"italic\">q</span> quarter years after the gym opens?</p>\n",
